text.section:
Accounts shall be rendered by the personal representative:
Within 9 months from the date of the appointment of the personal representative;
Within 6 months after the account referred to in paragraph (1) of this subsection and within 6 months after each account thereafter until the filing of the final account;
Upon termination of the appointment of the personal representative, as provided in Title 6, Subtitle 3 of this article; and
At the other times ordered by the court.
